'''寶石文蛤'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|''Gemma gemma''}}）是一種細小的海生[[軟體動物|軟體動物]]，屬於[[簾蛤科|簾蛤科]][[芽蛤屬|芽蛤屬]]。

寶石文蛤是最細小的[[蛤蜊|蛤蜊]]之一，只長5毫米。<ref>{{cite journal en|author=Sellmer, G P|year=1967|title=Functional morphology and ecological life history of the gem clam, ''Gemma gemma'' (Eulamellibranchia: Veneridae)|journal=Malacologia|volume=5|pages=37–233}}</ref>殼色呈白色或灰色，外邊及內邊有紫色。

寶石文蛤原產於[[北美洲|北美洲]]的[[大西洋|大西洋]]海岸，由[[拉布拉多|拉布拉多]]至[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.csc.noaa.gov/lcr/nyharbor/html/gallery/sggemma.html|title=Amethyst gem clam (''Gemma gemma'')|author=NOAA|accessdate=2006-03-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070504175214/http://www.csc.noaa.gov/lcr/nyharbor/html/gallery/sggemma.html|archivedate=2007-05-04}}</ref>，但發現它們也入侵到[[太平洋|太平洋]]海岸。<ref>{{cite journal en|title=Climate change, species range limits and body size in marine bivalves|author=Kaustuv R, D Jablonski & J W Valentine|journal=Ecology Letters|volume=4|pages=366–70|url=http://geosci.uchicago.edu/people/faculty/pdfs/ELett2001.pdf|doi=10.1046/j.1461-0248.2001.00236.x|year=2001|9=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060210135553/http://geosci.uchicago.edu/people/faculty/pdfs/ELett2001.pdf|archivedate=2006-02-10|access-date=2010-06-21}}</ref>

